scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: Book 1: dated 1853; inscribed by James M. Guthrie, president of the Louisville & Frankfort Railroad Company. Book 2: dated 1854; front cover indicates "Geo. D. Dicken's Book, 4025 shares." Book 3: dated 1852; inside front cover inscribed by "Geo. D. Dicken"; subscription for shares in the Louisville & Covington Railroad Company.
